These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, engineer, social-worker
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, taxi, tram
1. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
2. the social-worker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
3. the person driving the tram is between the engineer and the social-worker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Job         | engineer | software-developer   | social-worker |
| Transport   | taxi | tram | boat        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, almond-milk
3 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, guinea-pig
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the owner of the goat##7
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
3. the owner of the rabbit is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | 7up   | coffee   |
| Pet        | rabbit | guinea-pig | goat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, pumpkin, cabbage
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, boat, taxi
1. the person eating pear is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
2. the person eating cabbage is somewhere between the person eating pear and the person driving the roller##7
3. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
4. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | pumpkin | cabbage | pear |
| Transport   | roller       | taxi     | boat         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, doctor, scientist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, documentary, disaster
1. the scientist is not to the right of the doctor##8
2. the scientist is on the right of the firefighter##1
3. the person watching family movies is somewhere between the person watching documentary movies and the firefighter##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | firefighter | scientist | doctor |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | family | documentary    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, epic, disaster
3 different pets are kept: bird, hamster, mouse
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
3. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
4. the person watching epic movies is not to the right of the person watching comedy movies##8
5. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | disaster | comedy |
| Pet           | hamster    | mouse      | bird  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
