2. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5
3. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
4. the bartender is on the left of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Job   | bartender | analyst | entrepreneur |
| Pet   | ferret        | rabbit   | goldfish     |

