.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, soy-milk
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, software-developer, nurse
1. the software-developer is between the nurse and the person drinking soy-milk##2
2. the person drinking milk is not to the left of the nurse##8
3. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the nurse##8
4. the nurse is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | tea | milk | soy-milk |
| Job        | nurse      | software-developer    | paramedic |

