2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##8
3. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
4. the german is not to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | colombian | argentine    | german |
| Sport         | tennis  | ice-hockey | sailing |

