.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, spinach, garlic
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, spy, fantasy
1. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
2. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the left of the person eating spinach##5
3. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the person eating avocado##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Food          | garlic | avocado  | spinach |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | spy | fantasy   |

