.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, coffee
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, volleyball, sailing
1. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage   | milk | coffee        | fanta    |
| Sport      | volleyball  | sailing | ice-hockey |

