.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, milk
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, reading, woodworking
1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person drinking lemonade##7
3. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | milk | lemonade   |
| Hobby      | woodworking | reading | rock-climbing |

