.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, punk, r&b
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, golf, soccer
1. the fan of r&b is not to the right of the person who's sport is golf##8
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
3. the fan of r&b is between the fan of punk and the fan of techno##2
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the fan of punk is not to the left of the person who's sport is golf##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | r&b      | punk |
| Sport         | volleyball | golf | soccer     |

