2. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the owner of the dog##8
3. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
5. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | zucchini | lettuce | grapefruit    |
| Pet    | dog   | frog      | mouse |

