2. the argentine is the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person watching romance movies##7
4. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the polish##8
5. the polish is not to the left of the person watching horror movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | horror    | romance  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | argentine | polish |

