.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, puzzles
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, egyptian, dutch
1. the egyptian is somewhere between the dutch and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7
2. the nigerian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
3. the nigerian is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | chess | filmmaking | puzzles |
| Nationality   | dutch  | egyptian    | nigerian    |

 